@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="privacy-container">

    <p class="text-muted">
        This project is developed as part of an online course and is intended for educational purposes only.
    </p>

    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

    <p>
        By using this website, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
    </p>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>Information We Collect</h4>

        <p>
            The application may collect basic information that users provide while interacting with the system.
            This may include:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Username or account information</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Data submitted through forms within the application</li>
            <li>Basic technical information such as browser type or IP address</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            This information is collected only to support the functionality of the application.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>How We Use Information</h4>

        <p>
            Any information collected through this application may be used for the following purposes:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>To provide and maintain the functionality of the website</li>
            <li>To allow users to create and manage accounts</li>
            <li>To improve the application and user experience</li>
            <li>To troubleshoot technical issues</li>
        </ul>

        <p>The information is not used for commercial purposes.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>Data Storage</h4>

        <p>
            User data may be stored in a database associated with this application.
            Reasonable efforts are made to protect stored information; however,
            since this is a student project, it should not be used to store sensitive personal data.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>Third-Party Services</h4>

        <p>
            This application does not intentionally share user information with third-party services.
            Some technical components (such as hosting platforms or development frameworks)
            may process limited technical information as part of normal operation.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>Cookies</h4>

        <p>
            The application may use cookies or similar technologies to maintain user sessions
            and improve usability.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>Changes to This Policy</h4>

        <p>
            This privacy policy may be updated or modified during the development of the project.
            Any changes will be reflected on this page.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
        <h4>Contact</h4>

        <p>
            If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact the project developer.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>